0</PRE>
<P>
<H2><FONT color=#0070e8><A name=SECTION0001004000000000000000>Sample 
Output</A></FONT></H2>
<P><PRE>For map #1, the visible buildings are numbered as follows:
5 9 4 3 10 2 1 14</PRE>
